ComicInfo.Summary: Adapted from the Netflix original series! Trapped by lizard mercenary Kilara, Burnu discovers that there are more Kulipari than he thought when he meets the beautiful and deadly Wilka. He also discovers greater dangers than he knew existed in the form of Nahradhan, the great spider-god of death who has come to raise a vanquished evil in his plot to conquer the world! Kulipari creator Trevor Pryce, along with scripter Joshua Starnes and new superstar artist Sonia Liao, release the next chapter of Kulipari!
